summary: Various clothing from the game Path of Exile by Grinding Gears Games.
descriptionHtml:
Various clothing from the game Path of Exile.

Credits: Grinding Gears Games

Required Mods: [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/6709/?]DIMONIZED UNP female body[/url]

Female ONLY
Set Weight Slider to ZERO (type ShowRaceMenu in the console)

Use [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/64905/?]AddItemMenu[/url] mod to get the clothes or use "help" and "player.additem" commands in the [url=http://elderscrolls.wikia.com/wiki/Console_Commands_(Skyrim)]console[/url].

Clothing:
Scion Clothes
Ranger Clothes
Witch Clothes
Shavronne's Wrappings
Atziri's Splendour
Tabula Rasa
